My suggestion will be blitzcrank ad top because I was forced to go top and I ended up winning lane so hard even though I'm garbage. If you can time your abilities to proc the triforce properly you do so much damage, especially your e which doubles your base ad so your spellblade proc has insane damage. You become a bruiser with the best pull in the game, a silence and the ability to take towers faster than most adcs.

Top {{champion:53}} 
{{item:3078}} {{item:3053}} {{item:3110}} ( {{item:3068}} or {{item:3065}} ) {{item:3156}}  {{item:3009}} 

You need to play safe early but once you get a tank item and sheen you have some decent damage; and the ability to grab any squishy and be like 'your mine now fool'.

Oh and if you get caught out, both maw and steraks and mana barrier shields will activate, so you'll have insane lifesteal and a massive shield so you can often get back up to more than half hp before they break the massive shield and they can't just kite and wait it out since you grab them and then you can speed off with w and swifty boots once they're dead.

Something I've really wanted to try is
I don't know where {{champion:15}} 
