This build is very similar to what you would build on a shen. It works on Nunu though because your e slows and applies an atk speed debuff, your w provides a large movement speed and atks speed buff, q gives massive sustain, and your ult has high base damage anyways and works really well with the randulins. This build also split pushes really fast.

